data.description: Back on market due to buyer financing and no fault to the home or seller. Nestled in the heart of Zephyrhills, Florida, this delightful family home presents an exceptional opportunity for comfortable living in a prime location. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms, this spacious home offers ample space for your family. The open-concept living area seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining space, and living room, creating a welcoming atmosphere for gatherings and entertaining. The kitchen is beautifully updated with modern appliances, granite countertops, sleek countertops, and plenty of cabinet space. Luxury vinyl floors add a touch of elegance to the bedrooms, enhancing their appeal and comfort.    What makes this property truly special is its "Camden" floor plan, which includes an extra bonus room with a suite attached to it. This versatile space could make a great mother-in-law suite or a dedicated kids' area, perfect for multi-generational living.    This fantastic home is not only inviting but also conveniently located. You'll find yourself just 20 minutes from Wiregrass and 30 minutes from outlets in Lutz, 40 minutes from Busch gardens, offering an array of shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Additionally, the renowned Epperson Lagoon, a unique and luxurious aquatic attraction, is a mere 10 minutes away, providing endless opportunities for leisure and relaxation.    Step outside to your private backyard oasis, complete with a screened lanai, perfect for year-round enjoyment. The spacious master suite includes an en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet. With a two-car garage and a peaceful neighborhood setting, this home provides both convenience and tranquility. It's ideally situated near shopping, dining, parks, and top-rated schools. Low HOA fees make community amenities and maintenance affordable. Don't miss the chance to make this charming Zephyrhills residence your own.
